title: RKS Kettlebell Workout - x264 - MP4 - DVDrip
description:
Join the million's who melted fat and defined their body like never before with the clinically proven power of the kettlebell.

The #1 Kettlebell Workout System in the World!

RKS is a step-by-step full-body fitness program using a kettlebell that increases your strength, endurance, flexibility and cardiovascular conditioning, all while simultaneously melting away unwanted body fat.

System comes with a full instructional video, 16 Unique Full Body Workouts, Full Nutritional Guide, & Workout Calendar.

ALL YOU NEED IS THE KETTLEBELL! NO OTHER EQUIPMENT, NO GYM. JUST ONE FAT BURNING WORKOUT SYSTEM.

The Top 7 Reasons Why You Should Train With RKS

1. Only 30 Minutes a Day 4 Days a Week for a true Full Body Workout.

2. RKS is a progressive workout that is Fast and Effective that anyone can do!

3. RKS is a Fat Burning program that burns 22 Calories a minute and build lean muscle.

4. RKS works your core, shoulders, quads, hamstrings, back muscles, glutes all while burning fat and giving you cardiovascular stamina.

5. RKS uses Full Range of Motion Movements for Functional Fitness & Flexibility which tones and builds Lean Muscle.

6. RKS Burns calories up to 36 Hours AFTER you workout, even while you sleep!

7. With RKS Training, you can bring your kettlebell and train anywhere!
